## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Next.js 14 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Next.js API Routes (serverless)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (Prisma ORM)
- **Auth**: NextAuth.js (with 2FA)
- **Payments**: Stripe
- **AI**: OpenAI GPT-4
- **Storage**: Vercel Blob (encrypted)
- **Hosting**: Vercel

**Why this stack?**
- âœ… Fast development
- âœ… Scalable (serverless)
- âœ… Cost-effective
- âœ… Production-ready
- âœ… Great developer experience

