## ğŸ†˜ Need Help?

### Documentation
All answers are in the docs. Use this cheat sheet:

- **"How do I set up?"** â†’ QUICK_START.md
- **"What should I build next?"** â†’ NEXT_STEPS.md
- **"How does X work?"** â†’ ARCHITECTURE.md
- **"What's the business model?"** â†’ PRODUCT_PLAN.md
- **"Where are the files?"** â†’ DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE.md

### Common Issues
- **Build errors**: `rm -rf .next node_modules && npm install`
- **Database errors**: Check DATABASE_URL in .env
- **Auth not working**: Verify NextAuth.js keys, restart server
- **Type errors**: Run `npx prisma generate`

### Resources
- Next.js: [nextjs.org/docs](https://nextjs.org/docs)
- Prisma: [prisma.io/docs](https://prisma.io/docs)
- NextAuth.js: [next-auth.js.org](https://next-auth.js.org)
- Stripe: [stripe.com/docs](https://stripe.com/docs)

